characters.name: Lucie
characters.description: Lucie is a diverse contender who knows which brew makes you choke, heal or flee in fear. The arena has become her new playground for wild experiments.

ability1.name: Toxic Bolt
ability1.description: Projectile attack that deals 12 damage and inflicts Toxic.

ability2.name: Healing Potion
ability2.description: Throw a potion to target location that heals the nearest ally for 14 health and applies Revitalize.

ability3.name: Barrier
ability3.description: Grant a Shield to target ally. It absorbs up to 50 damage for 2.5s.

ability4.name: Clarity Potion
ability4.description: Throw a cleansing potion to target location, knocking nearby enemies away. The impact removes positive effects from enemies and negative effects from allies.

ability5.name: Panic Flask
ability5.description: Throw a chemical flask that deals 12 damage and inflicts Panic.

ability6.name: Roll
ability6.description: Roll forward and avoid incoming attacks.

ability7.name: Crippling Goo
ability7.description: Throw a vial of mixed chemicals to target location that deals 18 damage and inflicts Snare on impact. It covers the ground in a crippling goo that deals 80 damage and slows enemies over the duration.

battlerites.name: Weakening Toxin
battlerites.description: Toxic reduces incoming healing by 20% and outgoing damage by 10%.

battlerites.name: Vampiric Toxin
battlerites.description: Toxic heals you for 9 health over 6s.

battlerites.name: Stimulant
battlerites.description: Revitalize increases damage output by 12%.

battlerites.name: Companion Potion
battlerites.description: Healing Potion heals other allies for 4 bonus health.

battlerites.name: Alacrity
battlerites.description: Barrier increases movement speed by 33%.

battlerites.name: Blast Shield
battlerites.description: Applying Barrier causes a shockwave, dealing 10 damage to nearby enemies and knocking them back.

battlerites.name: Siege Barrier
battlerites.description: Barrier absorbs 8 bonus damage and duration increases by 0.5s.

battlerites.name: Adhesive Component
battlerites.description: Clarity Potion inflicts 30% Snare for 3s.

battlerites.name: Potency
battlerites.description: Clarity Potion heals 10 health when removing a debuff and deals 10 damage when removing a buff.

battlerites.name: Hysteria
battlerites.description: Reduces the cooldown of Panic Flask by 1.5s. Direct hits further reduce the cooldown by 1.5s.

battlerites.name: Chaos
battlerites.description: Panic Flask explodes upon hitting an enemy, dealing 8 damage and inflicting Lesser Panic to other nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Deadly Brew
battlerites.description: Panic Flask deals 10 bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Swift Roll
battlerites.description: Roll increases movement speed by 33% for 2.5s. Reduces cooldown of Roll by 3s.

battlerites.name: Sticky Goo
battlerites.description: Increases Snare factor of Crippling Goo from 35% to 60%.

battlerites.name: Agility
battlerites.description: Increases movement speed by 10%.

battlerites.name: Dynamic Solution
battlerites.description: Increases max range and radius of Clarity Potion by 10%.

characters.name: Sirius
characters.description: Sirius, a calm prodigy who uses the energies of stars and planets as destructive spells and healing powers. The prophecy was true and foretold the birth of the Zenith.

ability1.name: Crescent Strike
ability1.description: Melee attack that deals 8 damage. Your weapon charges over time. When fully charged, it deals 22 damage and inflicts Weaken.

ability2.name: Sunlight
ability2.description: Call down a beam of sunlight that heals the ally nearest target location for 14 health.

ability3.name: Celestial Split
ability3.description: Teleport to target location, dealing 10 damage to nearby enemies and healing nearby allies for 10 health.

ability4.name: Sunrise
ability4.description: Counter the next melee or projectile attack. When you counter an attack, teleport to a new location. You heal nearby allies for 12 health and fully charge your weapon.

ability5.name: Lunar Strike
ability5.description: Call down a ray of moonlight at target location, inflicting Petrify to nearby enemies.

ability6.name: Prismatic Strike
ability6.description: Dash forward and cleave nearby enemies. Deals 18 damage and inflicts Fading Snare.

ability7.name: Astral Beam
ability7.description: Channel a beam of light that deals 100 damage to enemies, heals allies for 100 health and heals yourself for 50 health over the duration.

battlerites.name: Debilitating Slash
battlerites.description: Increases Weaken factor by 10% and duration by 1s.

battlerites.name: Radiance
battlerites.description: Sunlight heals you for 8 health when another ally is healed.

battlerites.name: Sunbath
battlerites.description: Charged Crescent Strike hits empower your next Sunlight, causing 1 additional beam to heal the ally nearest the area for 12 health.

battlerites.name: Cosmic Reach
battlerites.description: Celestial Split deals 6 bonus damage and max range increases by {1}20{-}.

battlerites.name: Sunwell
battlerites.description: Celestial Split heals 8 bonus health. Healing an ally reduces its cooldown by 4s.

battlerites.name: Illumination
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with Sunrise illuminates nearby allies, increasing damage output by 20% and healing received by 40% for 3s.

battlerites.name: Sunscreen
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with Sunrise grants nearby allies a Shield. It absorbs up to 16 damage for 2.5s.

battlerites.name: Daybreak
battlerites.description: Sunrise can be recast for 1.5s to return to the origin location.

battlerites.name: Lunatic
battlerites.description: Lunar Strike can be recast within 1.8s to spawn Lesser Lunar Strike with reduced radius and duration. It does not affect enemies already affected by Lunar Strike.

battlerites.name: Moonlight
battlerites.description: Each enemy hit with Lunar Strike restores 1 Sunlight charge. Hitting at least one enemy empowers your next Sunlight, causing 1 additional beam to heal the ally nearest the area for 12 health.

battlerites.name: Moonstone
battlerites.description: Increases Petrify duration by 0.5s and reduces cooldown of Lunar Strike by 1s.

battlerites.name: Celestial Cycle
battlerites.description: Prismatic Strike hits charge your weapon by 50%.

battlerites.name: Gravity
battlerites.description: Each Astral Beam hit inflicts a 35% Snare for 0.5s.

battlerites.name: Saros Slash
battlerites.description: Reduces weapon charge time by 15% and charged Crescent Strike deals 4 bonus damage.

characters.name: Pestilus
characters.description: Pestilus, secret devotee of the evil Rasal, unleashes swarms of insects to infest and cripple his enemies. Advisor to the King of Quna, Pestilus is able to release his innermost darkest desires inside the arena.

ability1.name: Moth
ability1.description: Projectile attack that deals 10 damage on enemy hit and heals 7 health on ally hit. Inflicts Moth and heals you for 3 health.

ability2.name: Bloodsucker
ability2.description: Projectile attack that deals 30 damage on enemy hit, heals 30 health on ally hit and deals 15 damage to self. Cannot deal lethal damage to self.Hitting a Queen with Bloodsucker kills the Queen without dealing any damage to self.

ability3.name: Infest
ability3.description: Lurch forward, inflicting Infest to the first ally or enemy you reach. Heals allies and self for 8 health on hit. Can be recast to end this effect early.

ability4.name: Queen
ability4.description: Summon a Queen at target location, healing nearby allies for 16 health and 18 additional health over 5s.The Queen explodes after the duration unless killed by an enemy. The explosion deal 18 damage and inflicts Panic to nearby enemies.

ability5.name: Arachnophobia
ability5.description: Throw a spider egg to target location, inflicting Panic to nearby enemies.

ability6.name: Swarm
ability6.description: Grant a Shield to target ally. It absorbs up to 28 damage for 2.5s and spreads Moth to nearby enemies if destroyed by damage.

ability7.name: Scarab Pack
ability7.description: Summon and command 3 Scarabs to attack enemies or aid allies. A Scarab deals 26 damage on enemy hit and heals 26 health on ally hit. Scarabs stick to players for a short duration.

battlerites.name: Overlord
battlerites.description: Your movement speed increases by 7% for each enemy or ally affected by Moth. Stacks up to 3 times.

battlerites.name: Blood Leecher
battlerites.description: Hitting an ally with Bloodsucker causes you to deal no damage to self.

battlerites.name: Colony
battlerites.description: Hitting a champion affected by Moth or a Queen with Bloodsucker causes Moth to spread to nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Insectivore
battlerites.description: Hitting an enemy or ally affected by Moth with Bloodsucker deals 6 bonus damage to enemies and heals 6 bonus health to allies.

battlerites.name: Defiler
battlerites.description: Increases Infest duration by 0.5s. Drains 10 health from enemies and heals allies for 10 health over the duration.

battlerites.name: Spores
battlerites.description: Infest reduces damage and healing output of enemies by 50% and increases damage and healing output of allies by 25%.

battlerites.name: Scourge
battlerites.description: Allows you to Infest an additional target.

battlerites.name: Hive Mind
battlerites.description: Recasting the Queen commands it to fly towards target location. Reduces cooldown of Queen by 1s.

battlerites.name: Swarm Queen
battlerites.description: Queen spawns with a Swarm Shield that absorbs up to 28 damage and lasts 1.2s.

battlerites.name: Sacrifice
battlerites.description: Queen slows nearby enemies movement speed by 20% and deals 8 bonus damage when it explodes.

battlerites.name: Broodmother
battlerites.description: Increases Queen panic duration by 0.6s.

battlerites.name: Spiderling Venom
battlerites.description: Arachnophobia deals 8 damage. Increases Panic duration by 0.5s.

battlerites.name: Egg Carrier
battlerites.description: Arachnophobia bounces forward, causing another impact. The radius of the second impact is 15% larger.

battlerites.name: Lord of the Flies
battlerites.description: Scarab deals 4 bonus damage or healing and inflicts Fading Blind that reduces enemy sight range by 90%. Restores sight over Scarab duration.

battlerites.name: Disperse
battlerites.description: Releasing an Infested enemy inflicts a 20% Snare for 2.5s and pushes it back in the opposite direction.

characters.name: Blossom
characters.description: Blossom is a happy, bubbly young faun from the Silverdeep Forest. She has left her home to investigate a disturbance in the natural order. She is never far from her bird companion, Maxwell.

ability1.name: Thwack!

tooltipData.Name: Debuff
tooltipData.Value: Reduces target's movement speed by {slowpercent} for {slowduration}.

ability1.description: Throw an infused acorn that deals 10 damage. Your weapon charges over time. When fully charged, the acorn deals 20 damage and inflicts Snare.

ability2.name: Nourish
ability2.description: Send natural power to target location, healing the nearest ally for 12 health. Applies Butterflies.

ability3.name: Hop
ability3.description: Dash towards target location and avoid incoming attacks. Upon landing, become invisible, gain 20% increased movement speed and remove movement impairing effects. Using any ability ends this effect.

ability4.name: Tree of Life
ability4.description: Summon an immovable Tree of Life sapling that heals nearby allies for 12 health and 30 additional health over 5s.

ability5.name: Boom Bloom
ability5.description: Launch a boom bloom seed, dealing 15 damage. The seed will take root and bloom after a short delay, inflicting Stun on nearby enemies.

ability6.name: Gust
ability6.description: Summon a barrier of wind that pushes enemies away and reflects projectiles.

ability7.name: Dance of the Dryads
ability7.description: Launch into the air, then unleash a series of 3 piercing energy waves upon landing. Each wave deals 20 damage and inflicts Weaken.

battlerites.name: Weakening Pitch
battlerites.description: Charged Thwack! inflicts Weaken, reducing target's damage and healing output by 40% for 1.5s.

battlerites.name: Nature's Cycle
battlerites.description: Reduces your weapon charge cooldown by 30%.

battlerites.name: Kindhearted
battlerites.description: Nourish heals 2 bonus health when healing another ally. Butterflies heals for 2 bonus health.

battlerites.name: Fluttering Grace
battlerites.description: You move 10% faster for each nearby ally affected by Butterflies.

battlerites.name: Gift of Nature
battlerites.description: Hop causes you to leave behind a Lesser Boom Bloom seed. After 1.1s, the seed inflicts Stun for 0.8s on nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Hop and Skip!
battlerites.description: Hop can be recast for a Lesser Hop that travels a shorter distance.

battlerites.name: Nature's Presence
battlerites.description: Hop grants 15% increased damage and healing output to nearby allies for 3s.

battlerites.name: Cautious
battlerites.description: Increases Hop invisibility duration by 1s.

battlerites.name: Healthful Bark
battlerites.description: Increases Tree of Life health by 10.

battlerites.name: Refreshing Seed
battlerites.description: Tree of Life grants nearby allies 35% increased movement speed for 2.5s when destroyed or at the end of its duration.

battlerites.name: Bountiful Tree
battlerites.description: Whenever Tree of Life is healed by Nourish, nearby allies are healed for the same amount.

battlerites.name: Spring Growth
battlerites.description: Boom Bloom hits charge your weapon by 50%.

battlerites.name: Pollen
battlerites.description: Increases Stun duration of Boom Bloom by 0.4s.

battlerites.name: Puff
battlerites.description: Gust can be recast to launch a gust of wind. It deals 12 damage and knocks you and the targets apart.

battlerites.name: Growing Power
battlerites.description: Each consecutive wave of energy from Dance of the Dryads deals 8 more damage than the previous.

characters.name: Iva
characters.description: A scavenger from the outer realms. Iva has engineered her own arsenal of weapons. Firing crazy rockets or unleashing a storm of bullets is her way of greeting her opponents in the Arena.

ability1.name: Boomstick
ability1.description: Fire 4 bullets in a cone, dealing up to 16 damage.

ability2.name: ROCKET X-67
ability2.description: Launch a rocket that deals 26 damage. It explodes to deal 12 damage to other nearby enemies, consuming Oil to inflict Burning Oil.

ability3.name: Jet Pack
ability3.description: Fire up your jet pack and fly to target location. Inflicts Oil on enemies you fly over.

ability4.name: ZAP
ability4.description: Grant a Shield to target ally, removing all negative effects. It absorbs up to 28 damage and increases movement speed by 30%.

ability5.name: Tazer
ability5.description: Fire a shot that inflicts Spell Block. When Spell Block interrupts an ability, it inflicts Stun.

ability6.name: Tractor Beam
ability6.description: Channel a beam that drags enemies towards your position while blocking projectile and melee attacks in front of you.

ability7.name: Machine Gun
ability7.description: Fire a series of 20 piercing projectiles, dealing a total of 160 damage.

battlerites.name: Stockpile
battlerites.description: Rocket X-67 gains 1 ability charge but cooldown increases by 1.5s.

battlerites.name: Heavy Rocket
battlerites.description: Rocket X-67 hits inflict Fading Snare for 1.5s and the explosion inflicts Fading Snare for 0.7s.

battlerites.name: Boom!
battlerites.description: Rocket X-67 deals 4 bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Oil Blaster
battlerites.description: Jet Pack causes your next Boomstick to inflict Oil.

battlerites.name: U-Turn
battlerites.description: Recast Jet Pack to fly back to your starting location.

battlerites.name: Rocket Boosters
battlerites.description: Jet Pack increases movement speed by 40% for 2.5s.

battlerites.name: Blast Shield
battlerites.description: Zap knocks nearby enemies back and grants 25% Fading Haste for 2s.

battlerites.name: Hyperspeed
battlerites.description: Zap increases your Boomstick attack and reload speed by 120% while you're affected by the Shield.

battlerites.name: Durable Shield
battlerites.description: Zap absorbs 12 more damage on yourself and 16 more damage on other allies.

battlerites.name: Conductor
battlerites.description: Tazer hits bounce once towards a nearby enemy.

battlerites.name: Igniting Spark
battlerites.description: Tazer consumes Oil to inflict Burning Oil and deals 8 damage on Spell Block interrupts.

battlerites.name: EMP
battlerites.description: Tazer hits remove positive effects from nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Tractor Pulse
battlerites.description: Tractor Beam inflicts Stun for 0.7s to enemies caught in the beam when the effect ends and cooldown reduces by 3s.

battlerites.name: All Systems Operational
battlerites.description: Machine Gun inflicts Oil to enemies in a frontal cone when activated and launches a Rocket X-67 when firing the last bullet.

battlerites.name: Gunge
battlerites.description: Increases Oil factor by 10% and duration by 1.5s.

battlerites.name: Inspiration
battlerites.description: Increases energy gain from abilities by 10% and maximum energy by 25%.

characters.name: Alysia
characters.description: From the frozen north comes the ice sculptor Alysia. Her power allows her to wield ice with both grace and deadly precision. She can damage and freeze her enemies from a distance, while shielding her allies with ice. Obsessed with shapes and form, she left her icy fortress of solitude to seek inspiration in the arena.

ability1.name: Frost Bolt
ability1.description: Launch a cold bolt that deals 15 damage. Deals 2 bonus damage and adds Chill duration to enemies affected by Chill.

ability2.name: Ice Lance
ability2.description: Projectile attack that deals 22 damage and inflicts Chill. Deals 6 bonus damage to enemies already affected by Chill.

ability3.name: Arctic Wind
ability3.description: Inflict Chill to nearby enemies and soar gracefully to target location.

ability4.name: Glacial Prism
ability4.description: Grant a Shield to target ally. It absorbs up to 24 damage for 1.4s. When it breaks, it explodes to inflict Chill on nearby enemies.

ability5.name: Flash Freeze
ability5.description: Call down a frozen star at target location that deals 18 damage and inflicts Chill to enemies in the area. Inflicts Freeze to enemies already affected by Chill.

ability6.name: Ice Crown
ability6.description: Launch a fragile sculpture that knocks enemies back and blocks enemy attacks for 1.5s. When an enemy breaks it, a cone of icicles shoots forward to deal 20 damage and inflict Chill.

ability7.name: Frozen Gallery
ability7.description: Mark a path of frost. After a 0.9s delay, the path deals 35 damage and inflicts Freeze to enemies in the area, turning them into beautiful statues.

battlerites.name: Crystalline Lattice
battlerites.description: Glacial Prism absorbs up to 12 more damage and its explosion range is increased by 20%.

battlerites.name: Ice Breaker
battlerites.description: Ice Lance deals 3 bonus damage and breaks Freeze before dealing damage.

battlerites.name: Cryogenic Lance
battlerites.description: Increases Chill duration of Ice Lance by 1s. Ice Lance explodes upon hit or reaching max range to inflict Chill for 2s on nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Frost Nova
battlerites.description: Arctic Wind inflicts Root for 1s.

battlerites.name: Blizzard
battlerites.description: Increases Flash Freeze radius by 10% and reduces cooldown by 1s.

battlerites.name: Figure Skating
battlerites.description: Glacial Prism grants 60% Fading Haste for 1.4s.

battlerites.name: Twirl
battlerites.description: Arctic Wind can be recast to perform a short leap.

battlerites.name: Agility
battlerites.description: Increases movement speed by 10%.

battlerites.name: Inspiration
battlerites.description: Increases energy gain from abilities by 10% and maximum energy by 25%.

battlerites.name: Frozen Muse
battlerites.description: Whenever you inflict Freeze, your Frost Bolts are empowered for 3s. They deal 4 bonus damage and inflict Chill even on targets without Chill.

battlerites.name: Snowstorm
battlerites.description: Flash Freeze impact leaves a lingering snowstorm that deals 12 damage and inflicts Chill over 2.5s. The damage affects enemies with Freeze directly.

battlerites.name: Vandalism
battlerites.description: You can break your own ice crown with a single Frost Bolt to launch the cone of icicles.

battlerites.name: Permafrost
battlerites.description: Frozen Gallery inflicts Chill for 4s to enemies in the area when the path appears. Also increases Freeze duration from 3.3s to 4.3s.

battlerites.name: Wintry Blast
battlerites.description: Glacial Prism deals 10 damage to nearby enemies when it breaks and Chill duration increases by 1s.

battlerites.name: Arctic Cloak
battlerites.description: Hitting an ally with Flash Freeze applies Lesser Glacial Prism, absorbing up to 12 damage for 1.4s.

battlerites.name: Piercing Cold
battlerites.description: Increases Ice Lance range by 10%. It pierces enemies and damage reduces 30% per hit.

characters.name: Rook
characters.description: A mighty chieftain rushing into battle with a giant hammer in one hand and his dinner in the other. Rook likes to smash his enemies, with boulders, with hammers and even with his body. Once he goes berserk he turns into an unstoppable force.

ability1.name: Pummel
ability1.description: Melee attack that deals 10 damage. Successful hits reduce cooldown of Crushing Blow by 0.5s.

ability2.name: Crushing Blow
ability2.description: Jump into the air, then slam your mace into the ground. Deals 16 damage and inflicts Armor Break to enemies in the area.

ability3.name: Rush
ability3.description: Rush forward and slam into an enemy. Deals 12-24 damage and inflicts Stun. Damage increases with travel distance.

ability4.name: Berserk
ability4.description: Counter the next melee or projectile attack. When you counter an attack, become invulnerable for 1s and gain Berserk.

ability5.name: Boulder Toss
ability5.description: Toss a boulder to target location that deals 16 to nearby enemies and knocks them back.

ability6.name: Smack
ability6.description: Smack enemies with your meat to deal 12 damage and knock them back. Knocking an enemy into a wall inflicts Incapacitate.

ability7.name: Tremor
ability7.description: Jump into the air and slam your hammer into the ground 3 times. The shockwave deals 24 / 30 / 36 damage.

battlerites.name: Pummel Rush
battlerites.description: Pummel hits reduce cooldown of Rush by 0.4s.

battlerites.name: Squash
battlerites.description: Crushing Blow inflicts Stun for 0.5s.

battlerites.name: Weapon Break
battlerites.description: Crushing Blow deals 2 bonus damage and enemies affected by Armor Break deal 33% less damage.

battlerites.name: Rook Smash
battlerites.description: Crushing Blow deals 6 bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Endurance
battlerites.description: Rush cooldown reduces by 1s. Using Rush without hitting an enemy further reduces cooldown by 1.5s.

battlerites.name: Raging Bull
battlerites.description: During Berserk, Rush cast time and cooldown reduces by 60%.

battlerites.name: Frenzy
battlerites.description: Rush hits cause you to gain Berserk for 1.5s.

battlerites.name: Madness
battlerites.description: Increases movement speed bonus during Berserk by 30%.

battlerites.name: Giant
battlerites.description: Decreases damage taken during Berserk by 30%.

battlerites.name: War Cry
battlerites.description: Berserk inflicts 50% Snare for 3s to nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Crag
battlerites.description: Boulder Toss inflicts Fading Snare for 1.5s. Also reduces its cooldown by 1.5s.

battlerites.name: Crumble
battlerites.description: Boulder Toss deals 2 bonus damage and inflicts Armor Break.

battlerites.name: Earthquake
battlerites.description: Tremor inflicts Armor Break.

characters.name: Jade
characters.description: A mysterious gunslinger. Born with eagle-eyes and armed with a lethal sniper rifle, Jade's pinpoint accuracy is a serious threat for anyone who enters the arena. For close encounters, she prefers a combination of stealth and trusty homemade revolvers.

ability1.name: Revolver Shot
ability1.description: Fire a revolver shot dealing 6 damage.

ability2.name: Snipe
ability2.description: Fire a piercing bullet that deals 38 damage and inflicts Stun.

ability3.name: Blast Vault
ability3.description: Detonate a grenade that launches you into the air. The explosion deals 12 damage and inflicts Stun on nearby enemies.

ability4.name: Stealth
ability4.description: Become invisible, gain Fading Haste, and remove movement impairing effects.

ability5.name: Disabling Shot
ability5.description: Fire a shot that inflicts Snare and Spell Block. When Spell Block interrupts an ability, it inflicts Silence.

ability6.name: Junk Shot
ability6.description: Fire 3 piercing bullets in a cone, dealing up to 18 damage and knocking enemies back.

ability7.name: Explosive Shells
ability7.description: Fire a series of 4 explosive shells, dealing a total of 112 damage and 64 damage to nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Gunslinger
battlerites.description: Revolver Shot hits reduce cooldown of Stealth by 0.3s. Cooldown can't be reduced during Stealth.

battlerites.name: Deadly Focus
battlerites.description: Snipe deals 6 bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Shadow Shot
battlerites.description: Snipe hits heal you for 8 health.

battlerites.name: Surprise Shot
battlerites.description: Increases Stun duration of Snipe by 0.25s, and further increases it by 0.5s when fired from Stealth.

battlerites.name: Concussion Bomb
battlerites.description: Increases Stun duration of Blast Vault by 0.6s.

battlerites.name: Explosive Jump
battlerites.description: Increases Blast Vault max range by {1}20{-} and reduces cooldown by 1s.

battlerites.name: Blasting Pistols
battlerites.description: Blast Vault causes your next 4 Revolver Shots to deal 2 bonus damage and grant 2 bonus energy.

battlerites.name: Ambush
battlerites.description: Stealth reduces the cooldown of Snipe by 4s. Also increases duration of invisibility by 0.3s.

battlerites.name: Farewell Present
battlerites.description: Stealth causes you to drop a bomb that explodes after 1s, dealing 12 damage and inflicting Fading Snare for 1.5s to nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Through the Shadows
battlerites.description: Increases Fading Haste factor of Stealth by 40%.

battlerites.name: Desperado
battlerites.description: Disabling Shot hits instantly reload Revolver Shot with 6 ammo.

battlerites.name: Delight
battlerites.description: Disabling Shot hits heal you for 6 health and Spell Block interrupts heal you for 10 bonus health.

battlerites.name: Magic Bullet
battlerites.description: Disabling Shot pierces enemies. Also increases its range by 10%.

battlerites.name: Black Powder
battlerites.description: Increases Junk Shot knockback force by 25%. Knocking an enemy into a wall inflicts Stun for 0.5s.

battlerites.name: Shrapnel
battlerites.description: Explosive Shells inflicts 50% Snare for 1.5s.

battlerites.name: Agility
battlerites.description: Increases movement speed by 10%.

characters.name: Ruh Kaan
characters.description: Ruh Kaan was awoken when a grave robber desecrated the sacred crypts Ark’dun. Pursuing the trespasser led him to the Arenas where he is still tracking his quarry. He wields his dark powers to remove those who would stand in his way, taking great pleasure in consuming their souls.

ability1.name: Defiled Blade
ability1.description: Melee attack that deals 8 damage. Your weapon charges over time. When fully charged, it deals 18 damage, inflicts both Curse and Silence, and heals you for 12 health on hit.

ability2.name: Shadowbolt
ability2.description: Launch a dark bolt of energy that deals 30 damage.

ability3.name: Sinister Strike
ability3.description: Dash forward, then deal 16 damage to nearby enemies.

ability4.name: Consume
ability4.description: Negate melee and projectile attacks in front of you, inflicting Fading Snare on enemy melee attackers. Negating an attack fully charges your weapon and resets the cooldown of Shadowbolt.

ability5.name: Claw of the Wicked
ability5.description: Launch a claw that deals 10 damage and pulls an enemy towards you. Heals self equal to damage dealt.

ability6.name: Nether Void
ability6.description: Warp to target location and unleash a shadow blast that inflicts Curse on nearby enemies.

ability7.name: Shadow Beast
ability7.description: Transform into a shadow beast. Replaces Defiled Blade with a cleave attack and Shadowbolt with a pulling projectile attack. All your other abilities are disabled when transformed except Sinister Strike. Recast to end this effect early.

battlerites.name: Wicked Strike
battlerites.description: Increases Silence duration from 0.3s to 0.8s.

battlerites.name: Leech Blade
battlerites.description: Hitting Cursed enemies with Defiled Blade heals for 2 bonus health. Charged Defiled Blade hits also heal for 6 bonus health.

battlerites.name: Grim Edge
battlerites.description: Charged Defiled Blade deals 5 bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Agony
battlerites.description: Shadow Bolts deal 6 bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Affliction
battlerites.description: Shadow Bolt inflicts Amplify, increasing all damage the target receives by 20% for 4s.

battlerites.name: Nether Chains
battlerites.description: Sinister Strike inflicts Curse.

battlerites.name: Demonic Hunt
battlerites.description: Sinister Strike gains 1 ability charge, but increases its cooldown by 2s.

battlerites.name: Shadow Fury
battlerites.description: Negating an attack with Consume grants 2 ability charges for Shadowbolt.

battlerites.name: Gorge
battlerites.description: Reduces cooldown of Consume by 1s. Negating attacks further reduces the cooldown by {Can't represent GameValueList}s.

battlerites.name: Death Grip
battlerites.description: Claw of the Wicked cooldown is reduced by 1s and hitting a target further reduces its cooldown by 1s.

battlerites.name: Cold Embrace
battlerites.description: Claw of the Wicked inflicts both Root for 1.2s and Curse.

battlerites.name: Tenacious Demon
battlerites.description: Claw of the Wicked deals 3 bonus damage. Increases range by 12%.

battlerites.name: Hunger
battlerites.description: Activating Shadow Beast pulls nearby enemies towards you.

battlerites.name: Shadow Prowl
battlerites.description: Shadow Beast increases movement speed by 35%.

battlerites.name: Reaper
battlerites.description: Reduces your weapon charge cooldown by 30%.

battlerites.name: Night Stalker
battlerites.description: Your movement speed increases by 8% and is increased 8% further while your weapon is fully charged.

characters.name: Oldur
characters.description: Oldur, a mysterious creature able to bend time and space. He can mend wounds with powerful heals and reverse enemy attacks by freezing them in time.

ability1.name: Sands of Time
ability1.description: Launch a projectile that deals 12 damage and inflicts Time Bomb.

ability2.name: Rejuvenating Sand
ability2.description: Throw rejuvenating sand to target location that heals the nearest ally for 12 health and applies Rejuvenate.

ability3.name: Shifting Sands
ability3.description: Turn into sand and travel to target location. Heals allies you pass through for 12 health and deals 8 to enemies you pass through.

ability4.name: Time Bender
ability4.description: Negate projectile and melee attacks in front of you. Knock enemy melee attackers back and capture the first negated projectile within your hourglass. Recast this to launch the captured projectile.

ability5.name: Quicksand
ability5.description: Throw an hourglass to target location, exploding to deal 16 damage and inflict Fading Snare. Consumes Time Bomb to deal its damage instantly.

ability6.name: Stone Glass
ability6.description: Melee area attack that inflicts Stone Glass and knocks enemies back.

ability7.name: Time Travel
ability7.description: Target ally's cooldowns are reduced by 25%. That ally is removed from the fight for a short duration before reappearing at target location of their choice, inflicting Stun to nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Shared Fate
battlerites.description: Time Bomb deals 2 bonus damage and also deals its damage to nearby enemies when it detonates.

battlerites.name: Dehydration
battlerites.description: Time Bomb reduces incoming healing by 20% and outgoing damage by 10%.

battlerites.name: Rewind
battlerites.description: Rejuvenating Sand reduces ally's ability cooldowns by 8%.

battlerites.name: Renew
battlerites.description: Rejuvenate heals for an additional 15% of damage taken over its duration. Restores up to a maximum of 6 bonus health.

battlerites.name: Recreate
battlerites.description: Passing through an ally with Shifting Sands grants you and your ally a Shield that absorbs up to 16 damage for 3s.

battlerites.name: Chrono Shift
battlerites.description: Shifting Sands creates a Lesser Chronoflux that reflects projectiles and slows movement speed.

battlerites.name: Sandstorm
battlerites.description: Shifting Sands causes your next Sands of Time to deal 6 bonus damage and inflict Fading Snare for 1s.

battlerites.name: Time Walker
battlerites.description: Negating an attack with Time Bender reduces cooldown of Shifting Sands by 3s.

battlerites.name: Drain
battlerites.description: Negating attacks with Time Bender grants you a Shield that absorbs up to {Can't represent GameValueList} damage for 3.5s. Shield value is reduced for each negated attack.

battlerites.name: Stolen Power
battlerites.description: When you capture a projectile with Time Bender, your damage and healing output are increased by 20% while the projectile is stored in your hourglass.

battlerites.name: Sand Tomb
battlerites.description: Quicksand inflicts Root for 1s.

battlerites.name: Sand Struck
battlerites.description: Quicksand can be recast to throw Lesser Quicksand. It applies Time Bomb instead of consuming it.

battlerites.name: Time Burst
battlerites.description: Consuming Time Bomb with Quicksand deals 6 bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Reversal
battlerites.description: Time Travel heals ally for 50% of all health lost during the previous 2s.

battlerites.name: Eternal Dunes
battlerites.description: Each enemy hit by Quicksand grants 1 Rejuvenating Sands charge.

characters.name: Ashka
characters.description: A masked creature specialized in dark sorcery and pyro-kinetic powers. Casts devastating fire spells on his opponents and avoids close combat. Don't be fooled by his size, Ashka's inner demon strikes fear into all who face him.

ability1.name: Fireball
ability1.description: Launch a fireball that deals 15 damage and reapplies Ignite.

ability2.name: Fire Storm
ability2.description: Fire a series of 3 flame bolts. Each bolt deals 16 damage and inflicts Ignite.

ability3.name: Searing Flight
ability3.description: Transform into fire and travel to target location, dealing 10 damage to nearby enemies.

ability4.name: Flamestrike
ability4.description: Engulf target location in flames, dealing 20 damage and inflicting Stun to enemies in the area.

ability5.name: Molten Fist
ability5.description: Turn into a fist of magma and dash forward. Inflicts Snare and knocks the enemy back.

ability6.name: Firewall
ability6.description: Summon a firewall at target location. It blocks projectiles and inflicts Ignite to enemies that enter.

ability7.name: Infernal Scorch
ability7.description: Turn into a fire elemental and dash forward to deal 36 damage and inflict Stun. Leave a trail of scorched earth, dealing 24 damage and inflicting Ignite to enemies in the area over 4s.

battlerites.name: Combustion
battlerites.description: Fire Storm hits deal 2 bonus damage and spread fire to other nearby enemies, dealing 8 damage and inflicting Ignite.

battlerites.name: Wildfire
battlerites.description: Fire Storm launches {1}1{-} additional projectile but increases its cooldown by 0.5s.

battlerites.name: Heat
battlerites.description: Fire Storm can be cast while moving at 50% movement speed and 30% while channeling.

battlerites.name: Burning Feet
battlerites.description: Searing Flight increases movement speed by 30% for 2s.

battlerites.name: Blaze
battlerites.description: Searing Flight causes your next Fireball to deal 2 bonus damage and inflict Ignite.

battlerites.name: Fire Ward
battlerites.description: Searing Flight grants a Shield. It absorbs up to 15 damage for 3s.

battlerites.name: Eruption
battlerites.description: Increases Flamestrike radius by 15% and reduces cooldown by 1s.

battlerites.name: Inferno
battlerites.description: Flamestrike deals 10 bonus damage and inflicts Ignite.

battlerites.name: Ember Fire
battlerites.description: Flamestrike heals you for 75% of damage dealt.

battlerites.name: Lava Punch
battlerites.description: Reduces cooldown of Molten Fist by 1.5s. Hitting an enemy further reduces cooldown by 1.5s.

battlerites.name: Knockout
battlerites.description: Knocking an enemy into a wall using Molten Fist inflicts Stun for 1.2s.

battlerites.name: Fire Punch
battlerites.description: Molten Fist travel distance increases by 50% and knockback force increases by 25%.

battlerites.name: Conflagration
battlerites.description: Fireballs traveling through Firewall turn into Fire Storm bolts.

battlerites.name: Raging Fire
battlerites.description: Infernal Scorch causes your Fireballs to turn into Fire Storm bolts for 3s.

battlerites.name: Magma
battlerites.description: Ignite deals 2 bonus damage when first applied and reduces target's movement speed by 10%.

battlerites.name: Inspiration
battlerites.description: Increases energy gain from abilities by 10% and maximum energy by 25%.

characters.name: Varesh
characters.description: A being formed by the energies of others. Varesh uses his power  to weaken and disrupt his enemies. By combining his powers he is able to unleash devastating attacks.

ability1.name: Hand of Corruption
ability1.description: Fire a projectile that deals 14 damage, inflicts Corruption and heals self for 2 health on hit.

ability2.name: Hand of Judgement
ability2.description: Fire a projectile that deals 22 damage and inflicts Judgement.

ability3.name: Inhibitor's Guard
ability3.description: Grant a Shield to target ally. It absorbs up to 28 damage for 2.5s.

ability4.name: Wuju
ability4.description: Counter the next melee or projectile attack. When you counter an attack, teleport to target location and knocks nearby enemies away.Consumes Corruption to heal you for 6 health and inflict Fading Snare. Consumes Judgement to deal 6 bonus damage and inflict Silence.

ability5.name: Shatter
ability5.description: Spawn an exploding shard at target location, dealing 12 damage to enemies in the area.Consumes Corruption to heal you for 6 health and inflict Fading Snare. Consumes Judgement to deal 6 bonus damage and inflict Silence.

ability6.name: Kinetic Energy
ability6.description: Turn immaterial and dash towards target location. Spawns a Shatter shard under each enemy you pass through.

ability7.name: Powers Combined
ability7.description: Turn immaterial and dash forward in target direction, dealing 24 damage and inflicting both Judgement and Corruption. This effect repeats itself up to {1}3{-} times as long as an enemy is hit.

battlerites.name: Unlimited Power
battlerites.description: Consuming Corruption with Shatter increases Fading Snare duration from 1s to 1.5s and reapplies Corruption.

battlerites.name: Fervor
battlerites.description: Consuming Corruption increases your movement speed by 10% for 5s. Can stack up to 3 times.

battlerites.name: Silence
battlerites.description: Consuming Judgement with Shatter increases Silence duration from 0.5s to 1s.

battlerites.name: Devastation
battlerites.description: Hand of Judgement deals 4 bonus damage and hitting an enemy resets its cooldown.

battlerites.name: Return
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with Wuju allows you to recast it for 2s.

battlerites.name: Ruin
battlerites.description: Wuju inflicts Judgement on enemies struck.

battlerites.name: Zeal
battlerites.description: Applying Inhibitor's Guard consumes Corruption on nearby enemies, inflicting Fading Snare for 1.5s. Heal the shielded ally for 12 health for each Corruption consumed.

battlerites.name: Celerity
battlerites.description: Inhibitor's Guard increases movement speed by 25% and damage output by 15%.

battlerites.name: Wonder
battlerites.description: Inhibitor's Guard absorbs 14 more damage.

battlerites.name: Law Bender
battlerites.description: Each Corruption or Judgement consumed by Shatter reduces Inhibitors Guard cooldown by 2s.

battlerites.name: Fracture
battlerites.description: Ability charges of Shatter increase to 3 from 2, and Shatter deals 2 bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Inhibitor
battlerites.description: Shatter can be cast while moving at 75% speed.

battlerites.name: Kinetic Corruption
battlerites.description: Reduces cooldown of Kinetic Energy by 3s. Inflicts Corruption on enemies hit.

battlerites.name: Absolute Power
battlerites.description: Powers Combined repeats itself 1 extra time.

battlerites.name: Synergy
battlerites.description: While both Corruption and Judgement are active on an enemy, their factors are increased by 5% and both effects are reapplied by Hand of Corruption / Judgement when hitting that enemy.

battlerites.name: Inspiration
battlerites.description: Increases energy gain from abilities by 10% and maximum energy by 25%.

characters.name: Pearl
characters.description: A sage able to control the oceans and whatever creatures that lurk below. Pearl transforms water into volatile attacks, rejuvenating streams and protecting bubbles.

ability1.name: Volatile Water
ability1.description: Launch a projectile that deals 15 damage. Deals 22 damage and inflicts Silence if your staff is charged.

ability2.name: Healing Wave
ability2.description: Channel a healing wave to target location that heals the nearest ally for 21 health over 0.3s.

ability3.name: Dive
ability3.description: Dive into a pool of water and travel to target location. Recharges your staff.

ability4.name: Tidal Wave
ability4.description: Counter the next melee or projectile attack. When you counter an attack, heal yourself for 12 health and send out a tidal wave. It deals 15 damage to nearby enemies and knocks them back.

ability5.name: Bubble Barrier
ability5.description: Spawn a bubble barrier at target location that knocks players back. The bubble slows enemy projectiles and enemies inside it.

ability6.name: Bubble Shield
ability6.description: Grant a Shield to target ally, removing all negative effects. It absorbs up to 26 damage for 2.5s.

ability7.name: Jaws
ability7.description: Summon Jaws from the depths to devour enemies at target location, dealing 20 damage. Devoured enemies are removed from battle until Jaws spews them out, dealing 20 damage to enemies near the landing site. Can be recast to choose a landing site.

battlerites.name: Soaking Wet
battlerites.description: Increases Silence duration from 1s to 1.4s.

battlerites.name: Rippling Waters
battlerites.description: Firing Volatile Water through a Bubble Barrier increases damage by 3 and range by 25%.

battlerites.name: Splash Damage
battlerites.description: Charged Volatile Water explodes upon hitting an enemy, dealing full damage and inflicting Silence to other nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Fountain
battlerites.description: Healing Wave bounces to a nearby ally after healing, healing them for 6 health.

battlerites.name: Spring Water
battlerites.description: Dive heals self for 6 health and other nearby allies for 18 health when emerging from the deep.

battlerites.name: Ocean Tide
battlerites.description: Diving into a Bubble Barrier destroys the bubble and resets the cooldown of Dive.

battlerites.name: Riptide
battlerites.description: Dive deals 8 damage and inflicts Root for 1s at your starting location.

battlerites.name: Sea Bubble
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with Tidal Wave spawns a Lesser Bubble Barrier around you.

battlerites.name: Gush
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with Tidal Wave recharges your staff.

battlerites.name: Tsunami
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with Tidal Wave fires a volley of Lesser Volatile Water at nearby enemies. Each Lesser Volatile Water deals 8 damage.

battlerites.name: Ocean Sage
battlerites.description: Bubble Barrier can be recast within 1.5s to spawn a Lesser Bubble Barrier.

battlerites.name: Tasty Fish
battlerites.description: Bubble Barrier spawns a tasty fish that heals 8 health and increases damage output by 20% for 4s when picked up.

battlerites.name: Water Walk
battlerites.description: Touching a Bubble Barrier grants allies a 30% Haste that fades over 2s after leaving the bubble.

battlerites.name: Terror from the Deep
battlerites.description: Jaws maximum spew range increases by 25% and inflicts 33% Snare for 2.5s after enemies land.

characters.name: Destiny
characters.description: An elite sky ranger from the secluded, invisible city of Enza. Many years of rigorous combat training using Magi-tech weaponry makes Destiny an agile and deadly force to be reckoned with. Fed up with the strict regulations of living in Enza, Destiny often escapes the city to blow off some steam and have fun in the arena.

ability1.name: Power Blaster
ability1.description: Projectile attack that deals 16 damage. Successful hits reduce cooldown of Charged Bolt by 1s.

ability2.name: Charged Bolt
ability2.description: Hold to charge a projectile for up to 1.2s to increase damage and range. It deals 8 damage and inflicts Spell Block. When Spell Block interrupts an ability, it inflicts Silence.

ability3.name: Magnetic Orb
ability3.description: Compress yourself into an orb. Removes movement impairing effects and increases movement speed by 125%. Deals 14 damage to the first enemy hit and knocks them back.

ability4.name: Sky Strike
ability4.description: Counter the next melee or projectile attack. When you counter an attack, vault into the air. Then, jump towards move direction and fire a plasma blast at target location that deals 22 damage and knocks enemies back.

ability5.name: Plasma Wall
ability5.description: Deploy a Plasma Wall at target location. The wall reduces enemy projectile speed and inflicts Snare to enemies that pass through it.

ability6.name: Mega Sphere
ability6.description: Fire a huge energy sphere towards target location. Hitting the Mega Sphere with Power Blaster or Charged Bolt causes an explosion, dealing the fired projectile's effects to all nearby enemies along with 14 bonus damage and inflicting Fading Snare.

ability7.name: Pinball
ability7.description: Compress yourself into an orb and dash forward at supersonic speed. Deals {Can't represent GameValueList} damage and inflicts Stun. Damage is reduced for each target and wall hit, but is not reduced below 8. Bounces off walls up to a total of 3 times.

battlerites.name: Plasma Infusion
battlerites.description: Firing Power Blaster through a Plasma Wall increases the range by 30% and grants you a shield absorbing 10 damage on hit.

battlerites.name: Power Attachment
battlerites.description: Charged Bolt deals 1 - 5 bonus damage, based on charge-up duration.

battlerites.name: System Shock
battlerites.description: Increases Silence duration caused by Spell Block from 0.7s to 1.4s.

battlerites.name: Sizzle
battlerites.description: Plasma Wall deals 6 damage to enemies that pass through. Increases Snare factor from 25% to 40% and duration from 1.5s to 2s.

battlerites.name: Violent Revolution
battlerites.description: Increases knockback force of Magnetic Orb by 20% and it deals 4 bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Globetrotter
battlerites.description: Increases Magnetic Orb duration by 0.5s and its movement speed bonus by 20%.

battlerites.name: Dispatch
battlerites.description: Magnetic Orb can be recast to leap to target location, knocking nearby enemies back upon landing.

battlerites.name: Plasma Booster
battlerites.description: Allies that move through Plasma Wall have movement speed increased by 30% and are granted a Shield for 3.5s. The Shield absorbs up to 16 damage.

battlerites.name: Expansion Pack
battlerites.description: Increases Fading Snare duration of Mega Sphere by 1s and reduces its cooldown by 3s.

battlerites.name: Energy Conversion
battlerites.description: Sky Strike grants you a shield that absorbs up to 12 damage and absorbs an additional 8 damage for each enemy hit. Lasts for 4s.

battlerites.name: Blast Processing
battlerites.description: Sky Strike deals 6 bonus damage. Also increases its radius by 10%.

battlerites.name: Lasting Plasma
battlerites.description: Increases Plasma Wall duration by 0.5s and reduces its cooldown by 1s.

battlerites.name: Transformer
battlerites.description: Maximum amount of Pinball bounces increases by 2 and transforms you into Magnetic Orb at the end of duration.

characters.name: Zander
characters.description: When the famous theatre troupe "The Phantomime Masquerade" disbanded after a series of tragic events, their magnificent magician Zander vanished without a trace. Known for his unparalleled perfection in card trickery, teleportation, duplication and transformation, this distinguished illusionist has now returned from the dead to turn the otherwise ceremonial arenas world-wide into spectacular revelries.

ability1.name: Trick Shot
ability1.description: Throw two magical cards. Each card deals 6 damage to enemies, heals 5 health on allies, and heals you for 2 health on hit. Applies Hearts upon allies hit.

ability2.name: Grand Conjuration
ability2.description: A heavy magical projectile that deals 28 damage and pierces enemies. Inflicts Arcane Catalyst on targets hit.

ability3.name: Mirror Image
ability3.description: Turn immaterial and dash in target direction, leaving an Illusion where you stood.

ability4.name: Portal
ability4.description: Place a portal at target location that teleports allies one at a time, removing them from the fight for 1.5s before reappearing at a target destination of their choice. Teleporting an Illusion increases its duration by 1s and grants you the ability to recast Portal to pick its target destination.

ability5.name: Sheep Trick
ability5.description: Turn enemies inside target area into harmless creatures, rendering them unable to use any abilities for 2.5s. If the target takes 20 damage, the effect is broken.

ability6.name: Rabbit Form
ability6.description: Turn into a rabbit to increase movement speed by 80%, apply Hearts and remove any movement impairing effects. Knocks away nearby enemies.

ability7.name: The Prestige
ability7.description: Conjure a Grand Illusion at target position.

battlerites.name: Phantasmagoria
battlerites.description: Increase the health of Mirror Image illusions by 10 and duration by 2s.

battlerites.name: Showdown
battlerites.description: Grants self or allies traveling through your Portal a shield that absorbs up to 14 damage for 3s.

battlerites.name: Lasting Form
battlerites.description: Duration of Sheep Trick is increased by 0.3s and is further extended by 0.7s if the target is inflicted with Arcane Catalyst.

battlerites.name: Bunny Hop
battlerites.description: Recast Rabbit Form to dash forward, knocking back yourself and target enemy upon hit, interrupting any ability being cast. Inflicts a 1.2s Stun if enemy is knocked into a wall.

battlerites.name: Ace up the Sleeve
battlerites.description: Traveling through a portal resets the cooldown of Grand Conjuration.

battlerites.name: Arcane Conductor
battlerites.description: Increases the duration of Arcane Catalyst by 0.5s and damage taken by 5%.

battlerites.name: Poof!
battlerites.description: Your Illusions explode at the end of their duration, dealing 15 damage and inflicting a 0.75s Stun to nearby enemies. Grand Illusion explosions are bigger, deal 20 damage and inflict a 1s Stun.

battlerites.name: Lead Astray
battlerites.description: Sheep Trick inflicts Arcane Catalyst on targets hit.

battlerites.name: Late to the Show
battlerites.description: Teleporting yourself or an ally with Portal grants target a 50% Fading Haste for 2s.

battlerites.name: Transformation Sickness
battlerites.description: Decreases enemy movement speed by 20% during Sheep Trick.

battlerites.name: Heart Restoration
battlerites.description: Hearts restores 6 health over the duration.

battlerites.name: Stacked Deck
battlerites.description: Your first Trick Shot after using Mirror Image includes an additional card for both you and your illusion.

battlerites.name: Three of a Kind
battlerites.description: Grand Illusion receives a 3s shield when conjured, absorbing up to 20 damage and throws one extra card when copying Trick Shot.

battlerites.name: Around the World
battlerites.description: Increases cast range and teleport range of Portal by 20%.

battlerites.name: Arcane Shenanigans
battlerites.description: Allows Grand Conjuration to bounce once upon wall hit and increases its max range by 10%. Can still only hit once per enemy.

characters.name: Taya
characters.description: An exceptionally swift hunter wielding a razor sharp boomerang. By shaping the wind around her Taya is able to increase her speed and control her boomerang with deadly precision.

ability1.name: Razor Boomerang
ability1.description: Throw a piercing boomerang that deals 14 damage and returns upon reaching maximum distance.

ability2.name: X-Strike
ability2.description: Throw two boomerangs in an arc. Each boomerang deals 12 damage and inflicts Stun on the way out. Deals 6 bonus damage if both boomerangs hit at the intersection.

ability3.name: Haste
ability3.description: Gain Haste and remove movement impairing effects. During Haste, Razor Boomerang deals bonus damage and can be used while moving.

ability4.name: Wind Strike
ability4.description: Spinning melee attack that deals 12 damage to nearby enemies and knocks them away.

ability5.name: Wind Bomb
ability5.description: Throw a wind bomb to target location. The impact pulls nearby enemies to the center and creates a Wind Stream that lasts for 2s. Allies entering the wind stream gain Haste for 1s.

ability6.name: Tornado
ability6.description: Target ally is swept up into the air and becomes unhittable. They are tossed out of the tornado in their aim direction when the effect ends.

ability7.name: Companion Call
ability7.description: Your mount rushes to you from target location, dealing 30 damage to enemies in its path. When it reaches you, you mount and gain a Shield. While shielded, you can't be dismounted and you can cast empowered Razor Boomerangs.

battlerites.name: Breath of Air
battlerites.description: During Haste, the first hit of each Razor Boomerang heals you for 6 health.

battlerites.name: Cold Wind
battlerites.description: During Haste, Razor Boomerang inflicts Fading Snare for 0.4s.

battlerites.name: Cross Cut
battlerites.description: X-Strike boomerangs each deal 4 bonus damage, and an additional 4 bonus damage if both boomerangs hit at the intersection.

battlerites.name: Surprise Attack
battlerites.description: During Haste, X-Strike can be used while moving at 55% movement speed.

battlerites.name: Heavy Boomerangs
battlerites.description: Increases Stun duration of X-Strike by 0.2s, and an additional 0.2s if both boomerangs hit at the intersection.

battlerites.name: Tailwind
battlerites.description: Haste increases the movement speed of nearby allies by 50% for 2.2s.

battlerites.name: Gale
battlerites.description: Haste spawns a gale that slows enemy projectiles for 2s.

battlerites.name: Wind Fury
battlerites.description: During Haste, Wind Strike hits reapply Haste.

battlerites.name: Cyclone
battlerites.description: Wind Strike inflicts Stun for 0.8s to enemies knocked into walls.

battlerites.name: Vortex
battlerites.description: Wind Bomb spawns a vortex that pulls enemies towards its center for 2s.

battlerites.name: Tracking
battlerites.description: Razor Boomerang hits while mounted deal 2 bonus damage and extend the shield duration by 0.8s, up to 5 times.

battlerites.name: Inspiration
battlerites.description: Increases energy gain from abilities by 10% and maximum energy by 25%.

battlerites.name: Wind Stream
battlerites.description: Increases Wind Stream duration by 1s and the Haste duration it grants by 0.8s.

battlerites.name: Throwing Technique
battlerites.description: Increases maximum range of X-Strike by 15%.

battlerites.name: Turbulence
battlerites.description: Hitting an enemy with Wind Strike causes your next Razor Boomerang to deal 4 bonus damage.

characters.name: Ulric
characters.description: Sworn protector of the weak, devout follower of the Way of Symphony, and unwavering light against the dark. Ulric, trained in the holy Monastery of Resonance, has spent many years traveling the lands to spread the word of the Light. He joins the Arena now to demonstrate to allies, foes, and onlookers alike the primacy of the True Path.

ability1.name: Hammer of Justice
ability1.description: Melee attack that deals 10 damage. Your weapon charges over time. When fully charged, it deals 20 damage and inflicts Stun to closest enemy and 12 area damage to nearby enemies.

ability2.name: Holy Light
ability2.description: Call down a beam of holy light that heals the ally nearest target location for 14 health.

ability3.name: Intervene
ability3.description: Become immaterial and dash forward to slam an enemy dealing 12 damage. Dashing through an ally heals self and ally for 12 health, applies Favor, recharges your weapon and resets cooldown. Cannot hit allies affected by Favor.

ability4.name: Radiant Shield
ability4.description: Put up your shield and absorb projectile and melee attacks in front of you. Absorbing an attack charges your shield up to 3 times. Fires a wave of light in a cone dealing 12 damage and inflicting Blind when the effect ends if your shield is charged. Each charge increases the radius.

ability5.name: Smite
ability5.description: Knock nearby enemies back and replace Holy Light with Smite, a projectile attack dealing 14 / 18 / 22 damage. The effect lasts for 3 attacks or up to 5s. The effect can be canceled by recasting the ability.

ability6.name: Condemn
ability6.description: Jump into the air and slam your hammer into the ground to send out a shockwave. The shockwave deals 10 damage and launches an enemy into the air for 1.8s.

ability7.name: Aegis of Valor
ability7.description: Throw your returning Aegis. Deals 28-44 damage and inflicts Incapacitate, damage increases with travel distance. The Aegis lands on the ground on impact. Picking it up or catching it when it returns applies Divinity.

battlerites.name: Enchanted Weapon
battlerites.description: Hammer of Justice deals 3 bonus damage when affected by Favor.

battlerites.name: Cleave
battlerites.description: Charged Hammer of Justice deals 2 bonus damage. Deals 16 damage and inflicts Stun on secondary targets.

battlerites.name: Devotion
battlerites.description: Holy Light healing increases by 3 when healing self or allies affected by Favor.

battlerites.name: Faith
battlerites.description: Holy Light recharges 100% faster when Smite is active.

battlerites.name: Penitence
battlerites.description: Intervene deals 2 bonus damage and reduces incoming healing by 33% for 3s.

battlerites.name: Divine Protection
battlerites.description: Favor reduces damage taken by 10%.

battlerites.name: Initiation
battlerites.description: Intervene travel distance increases by 40% when affected by Favor.

battlerites.name: Light Speed
battlerites.description: Absorbing an attack with Radiant Shield increases your movement speed by 20% for 3s. Stacks up to 3 times.

battlerites.name: Halo
battlerites.description: Activating Smite grants a Shield. It absorbs up to 14 damage for 3s.

battlerites.name: Holy Fire
battlerites.description: The third Smite attack deals 4 bonus damage and explodes upon impact dealing 16 area damage to nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Holy Shackles
battlerites.description: Smite projectiles inflict a 35% Snare for 1s.

battlerites.name: Vindicator
battlerites.description: Condemn cooldown is reduced by 3s and hits refresh the cooldown of Intervene.

battlerites.name: Godlike
battlerites.description: All effects of Divinity are doubled.

battlerites.name: Light's Embrace
battlerites.description: Blocking an attack with Radiant Shield sends out a wave of light, healing nearby allies for 10 health.

characters.name: Poloma
characters.description: Poloma uses shamanic powers to guide life and spirits alongside her protector and loyal creature, Toki. A dark disturbance among souls has put Poloma on a new path, leaving her safety and home behind. Driven by her burning curiosity and extraordinary senses, Poloma now seeks her answers in the arena.

ability1.name: Soul Bolt
ability1.description: Fire a soul bolt that deals 10 damage and inflicts Soul Bind on enemy hit. Heals 8 health and applies Spirit Link on you and ally hit.

ability2.name: Other Side
ability2.description: Send target ally into the spirit realm, increasing their movement speed by 40% and making them immaterial but unable to use abilities. Heals nearby allies for 12 health when the effect ends.

ability3.name: Spirit Guide
ability3.description: Project a spirit guide that heals an ally for 16 health or deals 12 damage and knocks an enemy back. Can be recast to teleport to the spirit.

ability4.name: Spirit Rift
ability4.description: Open a rift, inflicting Spell Block to nearby enemies. When Spell Block interrupts an ability, it inflicts Panic.

ability5.name: Ghost Wolf
ability5.description: Send out a ghost wolf that deals {Can't represent GameValueList} damage and inflicts Soul Bind. It bounces to a nearby enemy after each hit, up to 3 total hits.

ability6.name: Pixie
ability6.description: Summon a pixie that follows you and mimics your Soul Bolt casts. Mimicked Soul Bolts deal reduced damage and healing.

ability7.name: Ancestral Spirit
ability7.description: Summon an ancestral spirit at target location and become immaterial for 0.7s. Deals 12 damage and inflicts Fading Snare to enemies and heals allies for 16 health. After 2s, the spirit departs to deal 36 damage to enemies and heal allies for 24 health.

battlerites.name: Specter
battlerites.description: Other Side causes your ally to become invisible for 1.5s.

battlerites.name: Spirit Walker
battlerites.description: Increases Other Side movement speed bonus from 40% to 50% and duration by 0.5s.

battlerites.name: Into the Realm
battlerites.description: Other Side heals 6 bonus healing. Also reduces cooldown of Other Side by 1s.

battlerites.name: Soul Theft
battlerites.description: Moving through an enemy during Other Side deals 8 damage and heals you for 8 health.

battlerites.name: Vengeful Spirit
battlerites.description: Teleporting to Spirit Guide resets the cooldown of Spirit Rift.

battlerites.name: Phantasm
battlerites.description: Ally affected by Spirit Guide takes 33% less damage and enemy affected by Spirit Guide takes 20% more damage.

battlerites.name: Ghostly Strike
battlerites.description: Spirit Guide deals 6 bonus damage and knockback force increases by 60%.

battlerites.name: Spiritual Wind
battlerites.description: Spirit Rift increases your movement speed by 40% for 3s when it inflicts Spell Block.

battlerites.name: Soul Essence
battlerites.description: Reduces cooldown of Spirit Rift by 1s. Spell Block interrupts further reduce cooldown by 1s.

battlerites.name: Silver Fang
battlerites.description: Increases Ghost Wolf range by 10%. The first hit deals 4 bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Dire Wolf
battlerites.description: The first Ghost Wolf hit inflicts Root for 1s.

battlerites.name: Affection
battlerites.description: Ghost Wolf returns to you afterward, granting you 5% energy and healing you for 12 health.

battlerites.name: Pixie Dust
battlerites.description: Pixie deals full damage and healing on mimicked Soul Bolts and cooldown reduces by 3s.

battlerites.name: Shimmering Bond
battlerites.description: Increases healing shared by Spirit Link from 50% to 70%.

battlerites.name: Dark Souls
battlerites.description: Increases damage dealt by Soul Bind from 30% to 50% and range of Soul Bind by 20%.

battlerites.name: Equilibrium
battlerites.description: The first impact of Ancestral Spirit applies Spirit Link on allies and Soul Bind on enemies.

battlerites.name: Condemn
battlerites.description: The second impact of Ancestral Spirit inflicts Stun for 1.2s.

characters.name: Croak
characters.description: His background is shrouded in mystery, his movements are supernatural and his reputation is whispered about. Croak loves to surprise his enemies, using his mobility to move in and out. His chameleonic stealth and flexible fighting style makes him exceptionally hard to catch.

ability1.name: Blade Flurry
ability1.description: Melee attack that deals 8 damage. Frog Leap and Camouflage increase the attack speed of Blade Flurry for the next 4 attacks.

ability2.name: Toxin Muck
ability2.description: Spit toxin muck at target location. Deals 6 damage, inflicts Toxin and heals you for 6 health on hit.

ability3.name: Frog Leap
ability3.description: Leap to target location and strike with your blades, dealing 20 damage. Can be recast to leap again.

ability4.name: Camouflage
ability4.description: Become invisible, remove negative effects and gain Fading Haste. Using Blade Flurry while invisible inflicts Stun. Using other attacks ends this effect.

ability5.name: Noxious Lunge
ability5.description: Dash forward, piercing through enemies to deal 12 damage.

ability6.name: Toxin Blades
ability6.description: Coat your blades in toxin, causing your Blade Flurry attacks to deal 2 bonus damage, inflict Toxin and heal you for 2 health on hit.

ability7.name: Venom Wind
ability7.description: Dash forward in the shape of a venomous wind, piercing through enemies to inflict Venom.

battlerites.name: Mending Toxin
battlerites.description: Increases healing effect of Toxin from 8 to 16.

battlerites.name: Spit Spit Spit
battlerites.description: Toxin Muck gains 1 ability charge but increases its cooldown by 1s.

battlerites.name: Triple Strike
battlerites.description: Frog Leap causes your next 3 Blade Flurry attacks to deal 2 bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Jungle Toad
battlerites.description: Frog Leap hits heal you for 12 health.

battlerites.name: Venom Strike
battlerites.description: Using Blade Flurry during Camouflage inflicts venom that explodes after 2s, dealing 8 damage to nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Cut to the Chase
battlerites.description: Increases invisibility duration of Camouflage by 1s.

battlerites.name: Noxious Reaction
battlerites.description: Noxious Lunge inflicts Root for 1s and reapplies Toxin.

battlerites.name: Trickery
battlerites.description: Noxious Lunge hits reduce Camouflage cooldown by 1.5s.

battlerites.name: Frog Frenzy
battlerites.description: Activating Toxin Blades increases attack speed of your next 6 Blade Flurry attacks. Also increases Toxin Blades bonus damage by 1.

battlerites.name: Momentum
battlerites.description: Venom Wind increases your movement speed by 40% for 4s.

battlerites.name: Lethal Toxins
battlerites.description: Toxin deals 4 bonus damage and reduces target's movement speed by 12%.

battlerites.name: Time to Strike
battlerites.description: Increases  Fading Haste factor of Camouflage from 30% to 45% and haste duration from 1.5s to 2s.

battlerites.name: Slippery Skin
battlerites.description: Reduces damage taken by 30% for 2.5s after Camouflage ends.

battlerites.name: Frog Slice
battlerites.description: Increases Noxious Lunge range by 30%. It deals 4 bonus damage.

characters.name: Freya
characters.description: Once a tribe queen, now a fearless contender. Her titanic hammers and overwhelming power of lightning is the perfect recipe for destruction.

ability1.name: Bash
ability1.description: Melee attack that deals 10 / 10 / 16 damage. Deals 2 bonus damage if enemy is affected by Static.

ability2.name: Storm Mace
ability2.description: Throw a mace that deals 10 damage and inflicts Static. Consumes Static instead if the enemy is already affected by Static, knocking them back and inflicting Incapacitate if knocked into a wall.

ability3.name: Spring
ability3.description: Leap to target location and gain Spring.

ability4.name: Electric Shield
ability4.description: Counter incoming melee and projectile attacks. Countering any attack pulls that enemy towards you and inflicts Static. Grants you a Shield when you counter the first attack.

ability5.name: Thunderclap
ability5.description: Jump into the air, then slam your maces into the ground. Deals 10 damage to nearby enemies and inflicts Static. Deals 6 bonus damage to enemies already affected by Static.

ability6.name: Charged Strike
ability6.description: Cleaving melee attack that deals 14 damage and grants a Shield for each hit. Consumes Static from enemies to increase the value of the Shield.

ability7.name: Lightning Strike
ability7.description: Leap high into the air, then strike down at target location. Deals 45 damage and inflicts Static. Deals 15 bonus damage to enemies already affected by Static.

battlerites.name: Static Hammers
battlerites.description: Bash hits on enemies already affected by Static increases the duration by 1s, up to a maximum duration of 6s.

battlerites.name: Twin Hammers
battlerites.description: Storm Mace gains 1 ability charge but increases its cooldown by 1s.

battlerites.name: Thunderbolt
battlerites.description: Storm Mace deals 8 bonus damage to enemies already affected by Static and Incapacitate duration increases by 0.5s.

battlerites.name: Tempest
battlerites.description: Storm Mace hits increase your movement speed by 35% for 2s.

battlerites.name: Thundering Spring
battlerites.description: Spring range increases by {1}25{-} and movement speed bonus duration increases by 1s.

battlerites.name: Lightning Speed
battlerites.description: Spring increases your Bash attack speed by 20% for the next 3 attacks.

battlerites.name: Electric Conduction
battlerites.description: Spring causes your next Bash to grant you a Shield. It absorbs up to 14 damage for 3s.

battlerites.name: Overcharge
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with Electric Shield inflicts Static on nearby enemies and grants other nearby allies a Shield. It absorbs up to 16 damage for 3s.

battlerites.name: Hammer Time
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with Electric Shield reduces Thunderclap cooldown by 4s.

battlerites.name: Torrent
battlerites.description: Thunderclap deals 5 bonus damage and pulls enemies towards you.

battlerites.name: Rolling Thunder
battlerites.description: Move forward during Thunderclap.

battlerites.name: Surge
battlerites.description: Reduces cooldown of Charged Strike by 3s. Hitting at least one enemy grants 25% energy.

battlerites.name: Thunderstruck
battlerites.description: Lightning Strike inflicts Stun for 1s.

battlerites.name: Positive Charge
battlerites.description: Increases your damage output by 15% while you have an active Electric Shield.

battlerites.name: Lightning Rod
battlerites.description: Each enemy hit by Thunderclap grants you Shield that absorbs up to 10 damage for 3s.

characters.name: Jumong
characters.description: Jumong is a trophy collector who has wandered the wildlands in the pursuit of a worthy challenge. No longer being content with hunting the great beasts of the world has led him to enter the arena, looking for a new type of prey. He traps his foes and ends them with a well placed shot from his mighty bow.

ability1.name: Hunting Arrow
ability1.description: Fire an arrow that deals 16 damage and charges your bow on hit. A fully charged bow enables you to recast Steady Shot, Black Arrow or Rain of Arrows.

ability2.name: Steady Shot
ability2.description: Fire a powerful arrow that deals 28 damage.

ability3.name: Black Arrow
ability3.description: Dash towards your move direction and fire an arrow that deals 8 damage.

ability4.name: Rain of Arrows
ability4.description: Fire arrows that rain down at target location. It deals 20 damage over 1.5s and inflicts Snare. The first salvo also inflicts Seeker's Mark.

ability5.name: Bear Trap
ability5.description: Place a trap at target location. When the trap is triggered, it inflicts Root on nearby enemies.

ability6.name: Prowl
ability6.description: Become immaterial and movement speed increases by 100%. Removes movement impairing effects. Running into an enemy inflicts Seeker's Mark.

ability7.name: Dragon Slayer
ability7.description: Hold to charge an arrow to increase its damage and range. The arrow deals 45 damage and pulls the enemy with it. Pulling them into another enemy or wall deals 30 damage to the second enemy and inflicts Stuns to both enemies.

battlerites.name: Perfect Shot
battlerites.description: Steady Shot inflicts Stun for 0.5s.

battlerites.name: Power Shot
battlerites.description: Steady Shot deals 6 bonus damage and knocks the enemy back.

battlerites.name: Prey Drive
battlerites.description: Steady Shot hits heal you for 8 health, and an additional 8 bonus health when consuming Seeker's Mark.

battlerites.name: Viper
battlerites.description: Black Arrow grants 60% Fading Haste for 1.5s.

battlerites.name: Precision
battlerites.description: Black Arrow deals 4 bonus damage and grants 4% bonus energy.

battlerites.name: Marksman
battlerites.description: Black Arrow hits grant 2 weapon charges.

battlerites.name: Crippling Hail
battlerites.description: Increases Snare factor of Rain of Arrows from 20% to 40%.

battlerites.name: Arrow Storm
battlerites.description: Increases Rain of Arrows radius by 10%. It deals 4 bonus damage over the duration.

battlerites.name: Deadly Trap
battlerites.description: Your projectiles deal 4 bonus damage to enemies caught in Bear Trap.

battlerites.name: Trapper
battlerites.description: Bear Trap lays down an additional trap in front of the first one that lasts for 3s.

battlerites.name: Disabling Trap
battlerites.description: Enemies caught in Bear Trap deal 50% reduced damage and rec50% less healing.

battlerites.name: Marked Prey
battlerites.description: Bear Trap inflicts Seeker's Mark.

battlerites.name: Panther
battlerites.description: Increases duration of Prowl by 0.5s and reduces its cooldown by 3s.

battlerites.name: Deadeye
battlerites.description: Dragon Slayer deals 5 - 15 bonus damage based on charge-up duration.

battlerites.name: Death Mark
battlerites.description: Consuming Seekers Mark deals 4 bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Agility
battlerites.description: Increases movement speed by 10%.

characters.name: Shifu
characters.description: Expert in the martial art of Ni'Shu and master of the spear. A highly mobile and dangerous duelist. His extraordinary combat prowess culminates in a range of deadly melee attacks. Facing Shifu is like walking into a tornado of spearheads.

ability1.name: Spear Slash
ability1.description: Melee attack that deals 10 damage. Successful hits charge your weapon, increasing the damage of your next Impale.

ability2.name: Impale
ability2.description: Lunge forward and thrust your spear in a line, piercing enemies to deal 9 damage. Deals 5 bonus damage per weapon charge.

ability3.name: Fleetfoot
ability3.description: You become immaterial and remove negative effects. Your movement speed increases by 35% and damage dealt reduces by 50% for the duration.

ability4.name: Kunju
ability4.description: Counter the next melee or projectile attack. When you counter an attack, teleport behind your enemy, heal yourself for 16 health, become immaterial for 0.5s, and gain Readiness.

ability5.name: Javelin
ability5.description: Throw a javelin that deals 12 damage and leap towards the enemy hit. Javelin can be used to pull yourself to a wall.

ability6.name: Tendon Swing
ability6.description: Swing your spear in a cleaving arc to deal 9 damage and inflict Incapacitate.

ability7.name: Whirlwind
ability7.description: Spin into a whirlwind dance and deal 112 damage over 2.75s to nearby enemies. Grants you a Shield and movement speed increase for the duration.

battlerites.name: Thrust
battlerites.description: Impale deals 2 bonus damage and an additional 1 bonus damage per weapon charge.

battlerites.name: Spear Lunge
battlerites.description: Increases lunge distance of Impale by 100%.

battlerites.name: Ceremonial Spear
battlerites.description: Impale heals you for 2 health and 2 additional health per weapon charge.

battlerites.name: The Spear is the Way
battlerites.description: During Fleetfoot, Spear Slash hits grant 8% bonus energy.

battlerites.name: Meditation
battlerites.description: Activating Fleetfoot near an ally heals you and your ally for 14 health each.

battlerites.name: Swift Feet
battlerites.description: Increases Fleetfoot movement speed bonus from 35% to 50% and haste duration by 1s.

battlerites.name: Poised to Strike
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with Kunju causes your next Spear Slash to deal 10 bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Mantra
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with Kunju causes your next Spear Slash hit to heal you for 14 health.

battlerites.name: Spear Slinger
battlerites.description: Hitting a wall with Javelin allows you to recast Javelin for 3s. Also reduces its cooldown by 1.5s.

battlerites.name: Javelin Master
battlerites.description: Javelin deals 4 bonus damage. Also increases its range by 10%.

battlerites.name: Dirty Tricks
battlerites.description: Javelin inflicts Root for 1.2s.

battlerites.name: Whirling Blade
battlerites.description: Tendon Swing deals 4 bonus damage and grants 15% energy when hitting at least one enemy.

battlerites.name: Spear Dance
battlerites.description: Increases Whirlwind movement speed bonus from 20% to 50%.

battlerites.name: Ferocious Stance
battlerites.description: Increases your maximum weapon charges by 1 and countering an attack with Kunju grants 1 weapon charge.

characters.name: Jamila
characters.description: A young assassin from the Shadowblade clan, Jamila suddenly found herself the new leader after the death of her mother, the previous matriarch. As the youngest leader in the clan’s history, some call her too inexperienced and undeserving of the title. Determined to silence those detractors, Jamila enters the arena to prove her mastery of the Shadow Arts.

ability1.name: Assassin's Cut
ability1.description: Three quick stabs that deal 6 damage each, followed by a heavy strike that deals 16 damage.

ability2.name: Shuriken
ability2.description: Throw a bouncing shuriken, dealing {Can't represent GameValueList} damage and inflicting Snare.

ability3.name: Elusive Strike
ability3.description: Hold to charge a dash for up to 0.8s to increase damage and range. It deals 8-18 damage and dashing in to a wall triggers a wall jump that inflicts Incapacitate.

ability4.name: Shadow Dance
ability4.description: Counter the next melee or projectile attack. When you counter an attack, gain Immaterial for 0.5s, turn invisible and increase your movement speed by 35% for 2.5s. Your next Assassins Cut while invisible becomes Shadow Slice, dealing 14 damage and inflicting Phantom Cut.

ability5.name: Hook Shot
