ability5.description: Launch a hook that deals 6 damage and pulls you and the enemy together. You strike after colliding, dealing 8 damage. Hook Shot can be used to pull yourself to a wall.

ability6.name: Deadly Blow
ability6.description: Strike forward with both weapons. Deals 22 damage, inflicts Stun and heals yourself for 22 health on hit.

ability7.name: Stalking Phantom
ability7.description: Summon a phantom that dashes forward, dealing 18 damage and stopping behind the first enemy hit. Upon arrival, it chases and strikes enemies in bursts for 18 damage up to 3 times.

battlerites.name: Go for the Throat
battlerites.description: Increases Stun duration of Deadly Blow by 0.5s and reduces its cooldown by 2s.

battlerites.name: Deadly Star
battlerites.description: Shuriken deals 3 bonus damage on each hit.

battlerites.name: Blade Swirl
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with Shadow Dance causes you to attack all nearby enemies, dealing 10 damage and inflicting Fading Snare for 1.5s.

battlerites.name: Quick Strike
battlerites.description: Hitting a wall with Hook Shot allows you to recast to perform a short dash strike, dealing 20 piercing damage.

battlerites.name: Agile Shadow
battlerites.description: Allows you to cast Elusive Strike while in stealth, increasing stealth duration by 0.75s. You are revealed while traveling and re-enter stealth afterward.

battlerites.name: Taste of Blood
battlerites.description: Shuriken returns to you afterward, healing you for {Can't represent GameValueList} health based on enemies hit.

battlerites.name: Drawing Blood
battlerites.description: Shadow Slice heals you for 10 health.

battlerites.name: Cripple
battlerites.description: Elusive Strike inflicts Fading Snare for 1s and Incapacitate duration increases by 0.5s.

battlerites.name: Push Off
battlerites.description: Increases the max range of Elusive Strike by 15%.

battlerites.name: Deep Wounds
battlerites.description: Increases Snare duration of Shuriken by 1.5s.

battlerites.name: Phantom Blades
battlerites.description: Phantom Cut deals 8 bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Firing Mechanism
battlerites.description: Increases the range of Hook Shot by 15 and reduces its cooldown by 1s.

battlerites.name: Momentum Strike
battlerites.description: Hook Shot deals 3 bonus damage and inflicts Root for 0.8s.

battlerites.name: Lurking Phantom
battlerites.description: Hitting a wall with Stalking Phantom's initial dash triggers a wall jump that inflicts Incapacitate.

battlerites.name: Inspiration
battlerites.description: Increases energy gain from abilities by 10% and maximum energy by 25%.

battlerites.name: Roundhouse Kick
battlerites.description: Elusive Strike can be recast to kick an enemy, dealing 12 damage and knocking them away.

characters.name: Ezmo
characters.description: Ezmo is an aggressive spell caster who can move quickly across the arena. Aradu, a powerful warlock summoned and imprisoned Ezmo but Ezmo saw his opportunity to escape when the warlock became too engrossed in reading his tome. He sealed Aradu's soul and mind within it and has been carrying the tome ever since.

ability1.name: Arcane Fire
ability1.description: Launch a bolt of arcane fire that deals 8 damage.

ability2.name: Chaos Grip
ability2.description: Hold to charge a projectile for up to 1.3s to increase damage and range. It deals 12 damage, knocks nearby enemies back and pulls enemies far away towards you.

ability3.name: Displace
ability3.description: Turn into arcane energy, travel to target location and reload Arcane Fire. Can be recast.

ability4.name: Arcane Barrier
ability4.description: Negate melee and projectile attacks in front of you. Negating attacks grants Arcane Fire charges. You gain {1}1{-} charge per 10 damage absorbed or {1}1{-} charge for each non-damaging attack.

ability5.name: Shackle
ability5.description: Manifest shackles at target location, dealing 8 damage and inflicting Root to enemies in the area.

ability6.name: Tome of Destruction
ability6.description: Summon the Tome of Destruction at target location. The tome mimics your Arcane Fire attacks.

ability7.name: Grimoire of Chaos
ability7.description: Throw the Grimoire of Chaos to target location. The power of the grimoire draws nearby enemies towards it. It explodes after 2s, dealing 55 damage.

battlerites.name: Exhaust
battlerites.description: Hitting the same enemy with 3 consecutive Arcane Fires inflicts Fading Snare for 0.4s.

battlerites.name: Warlock's Grip
battlerites.description: Increases Chaos Grip range by 20%.

battlerites.name: Disruption
battlerites.description: Chaos Grip inflicts Silence for 0.3s to 0.6s, based on charge-up duration.

battlerites.name: Collapse
battlerites.description: Chaos Grip deals 4 - 8 bonus damage, based on charge-up duration.

battlerites.name: Wreak Havoc
battlerites.description: Displace increases your Arcane Fire attack speed by {1}30{-} for 2.5s.

battlerites.name: Chaos Barrage
battlerites.description: Displace grants 1 extra weapon charge.

battlerites.name: Whizz
battlerites.description: Using Displace grants 60% Fading Haste for 2s.

battlerites.name: Feedback
battlerites.description: Recast Arcane Barrier to fire a projectile. It deals 4 damage for each of your charges.

battlerites.name: Spell Eater
battlerites.description: Negating attacks with Arcane Barrier grants twice as many weapon charges. For each charge gained, heal yourself for 6 health.

battlerites.name: Imp Rush
battlerites.description: Arcane Barrier increases your movement speed by 40%. Also reduces its cooldown by 1s.

battlerites.name: Undermine
battlerites.description: Shackle inflicts Weaken, reducing target's damage and healing output by 50% for 3s.

battlerites.name: Face Melt
battlerites.description: Arcane Fire deals 2 bonus damage to enemies rooted by Shackle.

battlerites.name: Bolted
battlerites.description: Shackle hits grant 1 weapon charge and increase Arcane Fire range by 50% until the next reload.

battlerites.name: Tome Of Restoration
battlerites.description: Tome of Destruction leashes onto nearby allies, healing for 16 health over the duration.

battlerites.name: Grimoire of Death
battlerites.description: Increases pull force of Grimoire of Chaos by 25%. It deals 10 bonus damage.

characters.name: Raigon
characters.description: Raigon, formerly the crown prince of Quna, is a skilled melee fighter trained in two-handed swordsmanship and martial arts. He hopes to break the evil spell cast upon his father and return home. For now, the arena serves as a decent place to find work and set the wheels in motion for his retaliation.

ability1.name: Sword Slash
ability1.description: Melee attack that deals 10 damage. Successful hits reduce cooldown of Retribution by 1s and charge your weapon, increasing the power of your next Retribution.

ability2.name: Retribution
ability2.description: Dash forward and cleave nearby enemies to deal 11 damage and heal yourself for 7 health on hit. Deals 3 bonus damage and heals yourself for 2 bonus health on hit per weapon charge.

ability3.name: Heavenly Strike
ability3.description: Leap to target location and strike with your sword. Deals 20 damage to enemies in front of you.

ability4.name: Parry
ability4.description: Negate up to 5 melee and projectile attacks. Melee attacks trigger Counterattacks that inflict Stun and projectiles are redirected at your aim direction.

ability5.name: Seismic Shock
ability5.description: Send forth a seismic shock, dealing 10 damage to the first enemy hit and launching them into the air for 1.4s.

ability6.name: Dragon Palm
ability6.description: Dash forward and strike to deal 8 damage, inflict Fading Snare and knock the enemy back. Knocking an enemy into a wall deals 10 bonus damage.

ability7.name: Wrath of the Tiger
ability7.description: Dash forward and strike to deal 20 damage. Upon hit, bounce between nearby enemies and strike them, dealing 84 damage over 3s. Afterward, dash towards your aim direction. Recast to end this effect early.

battlerites.name: Overflowing Power
battlerites.description: Hitting at least one enemy with Heavenly Strike grants you a charge of Slicing Winds.

battlerites.name: Headlong Rush
battlerites.description: Increases dash length of Retribution by 20%.

battlerites.name: Binding Light
battlerites.description: Retribution inflicts Fading Snare for 0.5s. Increases duration by 0.3s per weapon charge.

battlerites.name: Royal Descent
battlerites.description: Heavenly Strike deals 8 bonus damage and inflicts Fading Snare for 1.2s.

battlerites.name: Hawk Dive
battlerites.description: Heavenly Strike inflicts 50% Weaken for 2s.

battlerites.name: Acrobatics
battlerites.description: Increases maximum range of Heavenly Strike by {1}30{-} and decreases minimum distance by {1}50{-}.

battlerites.name: Invigorate
battlerites.description: Move at {1}100{-} movement speed during Parry. Heal nearby allies for 8 health when Parry ends.

battlerites.name: Riposte
battlerites.description: When Parry expires, perform a Spinning Slash. It deals 10 damage and inflict Stun for 0.3s.

battlerites.name: Duelist
battlerites.description: Negating any attack with Parry heals you for 4 health. Negating the first attack grants you a charge of Slicing Winds.

battlerites.name: Aerial Strike
battlerites.description: Seismic Shock can be recast to leap to the airborne enemy and strike them, dealing 6 damage and increasing air duration by 0.7s.

battlerites.name: Perilous Height
battlerites.description: Seismic Shock deals 10 bonus damage upon landing and deals 16 damage to other nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Soaring Speed
battlerites.description: Seismic Shock hits grant you 70% Fading Haste for 2.5s.

battlerites.name: Dragon Mastery
battlerites.description: Dragon Palm hits allow you to recast it for 1.5s.

battlerites.name: The Tiger and the Dragon
battlerites.description: Wrath of the Tiger ends with a Heavenly Strike.

battlerites.name: Agility
battlerites.description: Increases movement speed by 10%.

characters.name: Thorn
characters.description: Ancient folklore speaks of Thorn, the destructive apparition. Using its network of thorn-covered roots, it would whip, rupture and drain the life out of any living thing indiscriminately. Some say Thorn is just a story to keep kids out of the forests at night, others say it is an old lie used as a cover-up for misdeeds. Thorn’s presence in the Arena is both a mystery, and a very bad omen.

ability1.name: Root Claw
ability1.description: Melee attack that deals {Can't represent GameValueList} damage. Every third attack is a Root Grip that heals you for 6 health on hit and pulls enemies closer.

ability2.name: Leeching Thorns
ability2.description: Launch 2 leeching thorns. Each projectile deals 12 damage and inflicts Thorns.

ability3.name: Burrow
ability3.description: Burrow underground, increasing movement speed by 100% and removing movement impairing effects. Emerge from below after the duration, dealing 14 damage and inflicting Stun to nearby enemies. Recast to emerge early.

ability4.name: Evil Clutch
ability4.description: Grow roots from the ground and pull them towards you, dragging along any enemies in their path and dealing 12 damage.

ability5.name: Entangling Roots
ability5.description: Send whirling roots forward that deal 8 damage and inflict Entangle.

ability6.name: Barbed Husk
ability6.description: Grant a Shield to target ally, making them immune to disables. Melee and projectile attacks absorbed by Barbed Husk trigger a stinging volley that deals 10 damage to nearby enemies. While shielded, the target is unable to move or use abilities.

ability7.name: Dead Roots
ability7.description: Burrow and travel to target location, dealing 16 damage in a path and leaving a trail of dead roots behind you. The roots block projectiles, inflict Snare and deal 56 damage over 3.5s.

battlerites.name: Whiplash
battlerites.description: Evil Clutch hits allow you to recast to strike nearby enemies, dealing 12 damage and inflicting Thorns.

battlerites.name: Deep Burrow
battlerites.description: Burrow causes you to become invisible for the duration.

battlerites.name: Lurker
battlerites.description: Increases Burrow duration by 0.5s.

battlerites.name: Impaling Roots
battlerites.description: Moving under an enemy during Burrow sends impaling roots upwards, dealing 10 damage to the enemy after a 0.4s delay.

battlerites.name: Neurotoxin
battlerites.description: Thorns reduces target's damage and healing output by 20% for 1.5s.

battlerites.name: Hamstring Briars
battlerites.description: Thorns reduces target's movement speed by 20%.

battlerites.name: Parasitic Stems
battlerites.description: Thorns deals 4 bonus damage and heals you for 2 bonus health over its duration.

battlerites.name: Sinister Sap
battlerites.description: Entangle deals 8 damage over its duration. Reduces cooldown of Entangling Roots by 1.5s.

battlerites.name: Critical Backlash
battlerites.description: Each stinging volley inflicts Thorns on nearby enemies. Reduces cooldown of Barbed Husk by 2s.

battlerites.name: Regrowth
battlerites.description: Root Claw and Root Grip hits reduce incoming damage by 6% for 2.2s. Stacks up to 3 times.

battlerites.name: No Escape
battlerites.description: Burrow underground at the end of Dead Roots. The Burrow lasts for up to 1.25s.

battlerites.name: Creeping Roots
battlerites.description: Entangle spreads towards nearby enemies when the effect is broken, dealing 6 damage to enemies and inflicting Lesser Entangle.

battlerites.name: Fearsome Uprootal
battlerites.description: Each enemy hit by Burrow grants you a Shield that absorbs up to 14 damage for 3s.

battlerites.name: Grounding Grasp
battlerites.description: Evil Clutch inflicts Root for 1s.

battlerites.name: Branch Out
battlerites.description: Increases Root Grip range by 20%. Root Grip pulls enemies closer and deals 4 bonus damage.

characters.name: Bakko
characters.description: Bakko has a proud history as a heroic brawler, armed with both axe and shield. He uses his shield to protect teammates and outmaneuver enemies. Watch out for his earth-shattering dash attacks, as even calm warriors sometimes go berserk.

ability1.name: War Axe
ability1.description: Melee attack that deals 9 damage. Successful hits reduce cooldown of Blood Axe by 0.6s and charge your weapon, increasing the damage of your next Blood Axe.

ability2.name: Blood Axe
ability2.description: Throw an axe that deals 16 damage. Deals 4 bonus damage per weapon charge.

ability3.name: Valiant Leap
ability3.description: Leap into the air and strike down at target location, dealing 22 damage to nearby enemies and inflicting Snare.

ability4.name: Bulwark
ability4.description: Put up your shield and block projectile and melee attacks in front of you. Reflects enemy projectiles and inflicts Stun on enemy melee attackers.

ability5.name: Shield Dash
ability5.description: Dash forward and grab an enemy, pushing them in front of you. Pushing them into a wall deals 12 damage and inflicts Stun.

ability6.name: War Shout
ability6.description: Let loose a war shout that grants a Shield to nearby allies, absorbing up to 40 damage for 3s.

ability7.name: Heroic Charge
ability7.description: Rush forward and grab an enemy, dealing 35 damage and pushing them in front of you. Deals 28 area damage and inflicts Stun when reaching max range or colliding with a wall or another enemy.

battlerites.name: Axe and Shield
battlerites.description: War Axe hits reduce the cooldown of Bulwark by 1s.

battlerites.name: The Red Axe
battlerites.description: Blood Axe hits heal you for 4 health plus 2 additional health per weapon charge.

battlerites.name: Howling Axes
battlerites.description: Blood Axe hits reduce its cooldown by 1.5s.

battlerites.name: Hamstring
battlerites.description: Blood Axe inflicts Fading Snare for 1.2s.

battlerites.name: Warlord's Axe
battlerites.description: Blood Axe deals 2 bonus damage and an additional 1 bonus damage per weapon charge.

battlerites.name: Adrenaline Rush
battlerites.description: Valiant Leap causes your next War Axe hit to deal 9 bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Bravery
battlerites.description: Valiant Leap grants 33% damage reduction for 2.5s to nearby allies.

battlerites.name: Heroic Leap
battlerites.description: Increases max range of Valiant Leap by {1}20{-}. It deals 3 bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Shield Bash
battlerites.description: Bulwark can be recast to use Shield Bash. It deals 6 damage and inflicts 50% Weaken for 2s.

battlerites.name: Mobile Defence
battlerites.description: Bulwark increases movement speed by 60%.

battlerites.name: Dizzying Dash
battlerites.description: Shield Dash inflicts 15% Snare for 2.5s. Pushing an enemy into a wall deals 6 bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Adrenaline Slam
battlerites.description: Hitting an enemy with Shield Dash causes your next War Axe hit to deal 9 bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Raging Ram
battlerites.description: Increases range of Shield Dash by {1}25{-} and reduces cooldown by 1s.

battlerites.name: Rampage
battlerites.description: War Shout increases attack speed of War Axe and Blood Axe by {1}33{-} and movement speed by 15% for 4s.

battlerites.name: Mammoth Stomp
battlerites.description: Increases Stun duration of Heroic Charge by 0.75s.

battlerites.name: Inspiration
battlerites.description: Increases energy gain from abilities by 10% and maximum energy by 25%.
